        "text_block_hBNnei": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "One Piece Swimsuits That Flatter, Support & Stay On",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Our one piece swimsuit collection is designed for women who want more than just a beautiful suit - they want performance, support, and timeless style that moves with them. Whether you’re surfing, swimming, paddling, or lounging between sessions, these one pieces sculpt your shape while keeping you confident and comfortable.</p><p>From sleek sleeveless one piece swimsuits to long sleeve one piece styles that offer extra coverage and sun protection, every design is created with real movement in mind. Each suit is made from luxurious recycled Italian fabric, double-lined for opacity and support, and crafted with clever panel placement that defines your waist and smooths your silhouette - without the need for padding.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
