    "image_with_text_Yer8pT": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/laotratuvera_by_michaelxscn_High_Res__Sulawesi_Onyx4_1_edited.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Women Love Ocean Soul One Piece Swimsuits",
        "text": "<h4>A Style for Every Water Woman</h4><p>We know one piece swimwear isn’t one-size-fits-all, which is why our collection includes:</p><p> Ideal for surfing, SUP, and all-day sun protection.<br/></p><p>Streamlined and versatile, perfect for swimming laps or styling as a bodysuit.<br/></p><p>Timeless, flattering silhouettes for all occasions.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_G8XPYd": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/amphibiansoul_by_ocean_lembongan14_bfd6913e-83f0-40e8-af63-63a7b525a826.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable, Ethical & Built to Last",
        "text": "<p>Every Ocean Soul one piece is made from Econyl® regenerated fabric, created from rescued fishing nets and ocean waste. We produce in small batches in Bali, ensuring fair wages and minimising waste. The result? A swimsuit that’s as kind to the planet as it is to your skin.</p><p>Our one pieces last twice as long as standard swimwear, resisting fading, stretching, and sagging.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_gLA8HN": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/DSC04997__lorrainek8_photog_beavegashoots.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "UPF 50+ Sun Protection",
        "text": "<p>Our UPF 50+ swimsuits give you built-in sun protection without chemical treatments. Especially in long sleeve designs, they provide coverage that’s essential for long hours in the water.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_TmNY6f": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/merry_amber4.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sculpting Fit Without Padding",
        "text": "<p>No bulky inserts here - our supportive one piece swimsuits use strategic paneling, a cinched waist, and double lining to smooth, lift, and hold you in all the right places. The high-cut leg subtly elongates your silhouette while providing secure coverage.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_q4FULh": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/MG_7759_Last_Resort_Federico_Vanno_Liquid_Barrel_copy.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Surf-Tested Swimwear",
        "text": "<p>Our one pieces aren’t just for sunbathing - they’re made to move. Surf-tested and active-ready, they stay on through duck dives, wipeouts, and long paddles. Whether you’re catching waves, exploring reefs, or chasing your kids on the beach, you can rely on your suit to stay in place.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
