    "rich_text_xtwcWg": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_block_7xNqFN": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Ocean Soul One Piece Swimsuits Are Made for Real Life in the Water",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<h4>Sun-Safe and Sea-Ready: UPF 50+ Swimwear</h4><p>Ocean Soul Swimwear one pieces are made with UPF 50+ sun protection, built directly into the fabric — no chemical finishes required. Whether you’re out on the surfboard, paddling with your SUP crew, or spending hours at the beach with your kids, you can rely on your suit to protect you from harmful UV rays without reapplying sunscreen every 20 minutes.</p><h4></h4><h4>Long Sleeve, Sleeveless & Classic One Pieces</h4><h4></h4><h4></h4><p></p><p></p><p>We’ve created multiple silhouettes to suit every body and every adventure:</p><p></p><p>Perfect for surfing, paddling, or full sun protection. Our long sleeve styles offer coverage, security, and a chic surf aesthetic.</p><p> Ideal for freediving, lap swimming, or minimalist sun-lovers. These are cut for performance with clean lines and open-back options.<br/></p><p> Flattering, timeless, and versatile enough to wear as a bodysuit under a skirt or pants. Perfect for holidays, beach days, and beyond.</p><p></p><p></p><p>Whichever style you choose, you’ll get the same Ocean Soul signature fit: sculpting, supportive, and smoothing — without compromise.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><h4></h4><h4></h4><h4>Made from Sustainable Recycled Fabric</h4><p>Our entire one piece collection is made from <strong>regenerated ECONYL® yarn</strong>, a performance fabric made from rescued fishing nets and ocean plastics. This sustainable material is not only eco-conscious, but also:</p><p>Soft and breathable<br/>Durable and resistant to chlorine and salt<br/>Long-lasting with minimal fade or sag<br/><br/></p><p>Because we double-line our suits and use no foam or padding, you get natural support that lasts — and never loses shape.</p><p></p><h4></h4><h4>Thoughtfully Designed to Flatter</h4><p>From the moment you step into an Ocean Soul swimsuit, you’ll notice the difference. Our designs are:</p><p>cleverly designed to contour your waist</p><p>Double-lined for smoothing support</p><p>Minimalist in colour for a clean, slimming look</p><p>Finished with premium YKK zips for long-lasting performance</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>- Unlike fast fashion swimwear, our suits are made to empower — not distract. You won’t need to constantly adjust, tug, or worry about coverage. Just put it on, and go live your day.</p><h4></h4><h4>Built for Water Women</h4><p>Our one pieces are performance-tested in the water, staying on through duck dives, dives, and wipeouts. Whether you’re surfing reef breaks, gliding through a freedive, or teaching your kids to swim, you can count on your Ocean Soul suit to stay secure and comfortable.</p><p>It’s why our one piece swimsuits are trusted by freedivers, surfers, athletes, and mums alike.</p><h4></h4><h4></h4><h4>The One Piece That Changes Everything</h4><p>If you’ve been searching for a flattering one piece swimsuit that:</p><p>Sculpts your shape without uncomfortable padding</p><p>Protects your skin from sun damage</p><p>Stays on during real activity</p><p>Feels beautiful on the body</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Aligns with your values for sustainability and ethical fashion</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
